    narrator "{i}Elia stands. Looks at Elisira, who has rematerialized near the hull breach with a portable console. Looks at Nyx, examining the resonance worker with clinical attention. Looks at the cargo bay-the damage, the blood, the evidence of violence that will need to be cleaned and reported and explained in forms that exist specifically to make explaining difficult.{/i}"
