    narrator "{i}Vesper finds her there an hour later. The repairs are underway. The pirates are secured. The paperwork is multiplying with the organic determination of bureaucracy given enough raw material. Pol's body has been recovered. They'll return it to his station. His children will receive a form.{/i}"
